body.description: Dress up as Gabby from Gabby’s Dollhouse with the Magical Musical Ears! These interactive cat ears look just like the ones Gabby wears in the show. Slide the Magical Musical Ears on and get ready for adventure! Featuring lights and over 10 sounds, phrases and songs, you’ll have endless amounts of fun! Simply press one of the pink sparkly ears to turn them on, then pinch the left ear to hear phrases from Gabby. To activate sound effects and songs from the show, pinch the right ear and have a dance party as the music plays! Enter Meow Mode by pressing both ears at the same time for pulsating lights and cat-tastic meows! The Magical Musical Ears are the perfect accessory to bring the memorable shrink-me moment from the show to life. Wearing your own pair of cat ears, you’ll feel just like Gabby! Use your imagination to create and play out your adventures as Gabby with the Gabby’s Dollhouse Magical Musical Ears!

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: DreamWorks Gabby’s Dollhouse Interactive Magical Musical Cat Ears Get ready for adventure with DreamWorks Gabby’s Dollhouse Magical Musical Ears! Featuring authentic details, these interactive cat ears look just like the ones Gabby wears in the NETFLIX original series. With 3 modes of play, lights and over 10 sounds, phrases and songs from the show, you’ll have hours of fun playing out your own Gabby’s Dollhouse adventures. Slide on the Magical Musical Ears and pinch the left ear to hear phrases from Gabby! For sound effects and songs, pinch the right ear and have a dance party! Pinch both ears at the same time for pulsing lights and cat-tastic meows – it’s so much fun! Create your own adventures dressed as Gabby with the Magical Musical Ears! Includes: 1 Magical Musical Ears 1 Instruction Sheet

Dress up as Gabby! The Magical Musical Ears bring the magic of Gabby’s Dollhouse to life! With pink sparkly details, pointy ears and a black patch on one ear, they look just like the cat ears Gabby wears in the show. Slide them on, re-enact the show’s shrink-me moment and feel just like Gabby as you play out endless cat-tastic adventures! Lights, Music & Sounds A pinch on the left, pinch, pinch on the right! Wearing your own pair of cat ears, you’ll have hours of role-play fun. The Magical Musical Ears feature over 10 sounds, phrases, and songs straight from Gabby’s Dollhouse. They even light up for memorable pretend play storytelling! Batteries are included, so you can play out of the box. 3 Fun Ways to Play With 3 modes of play, the Magical Musical Ears are the purrfect accessory to play out your own adventures inspired by the show. Pinch the left ear and you’ll hear phrases from Gabby herself! For songs and music, pinch the right ear and have a dance party! Then, press both ears for pulsing lights and meows – it’s so much fun!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 24, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Gabby’s Dollhouse Sprinkle Party Sweet Treat Set - A Delightful Addition to Playtime
reviews.reviewText: I recently introduced the Gabby’s Dollhouse Sprinkle Party Sweet Treat Set to my child's playtime, and it has quickly become a favorite. This charming playset, inspired by the popular Gabby’s Dollhouse series, offers a delightful and imaginative way for children to engage in pretend play, fostering creativity and enjoyment.The standout feature of the Sprinkle Party Sweet Treat Set is its vibrant and whimsical design. The set is adorned with details inspired by the colorful world of Gabby’s Dollhouse, capturing the attention and imagination of young children. The playful and inviting aesthetic adds an element of joy to playtime.The variety of sweet treats included in the set allows for imaginative storytelling and role-playing. From cupcakes and cookies to ice cream cones and more, each piece is intricately designed to resemble delectable desserts. This diversity encourages children to explore different scenarios, creating a dynamic and engaging play experience.The interactive elements of the Sprinkle Party Sweet Treat Set enhance its play value. With features like a spinning cake stand and movable pieces, children can actively participate in creating their own sweet party scenes. This interactivity promotes fine motor skills and coordination, contributing to a holistic playtime experience.Durability is a key consideration for toys, especially those designed for younger children, and the Gabby’s Dollhouse playset does not disappoint. The sturdy construction of the Sprinkle Party Sweet Treat Set ensures that it can withstand the enthusiastic play of little hands, providing long-lasting enjoyment.Compatibility with other Gabby’s Dollhouse playsets adds to the versatility of the Sprinkle Party Sweet Treat Set. Children can mix and match different sets to create a customized and expansive Dollhouse world, fostering a sense of creativity and imagination as they build and explore.In conclusion, the Gabby’s Dollhouse Sprinkle Party Sweet Treat Set is a delightful addition to playtime. Its vibrant design, variety of sweet treats, interactive features, durability, and compatibility with other playsets make it a standout choice for young children. Bring the joy of Gabby’s Dollhouse to life with the Sprinkle Party Sweet Treat Set, offering hours of imaginative play and endless fun.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Very cute and well made!
reviews.reviewText: I bought these foe my 4 year old daughter foe Christmas and she loves them! The ears light up and sing or talk when you press them. They are not too loud and they are made very sturdy. I have worn them and she dropped them a few times and they still work great! This is worth every penny for the Gabby lovers in your life!

reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars A little disappointed in the quality
reviews.reviewText: My daughter was so excited to get this gift for Christmas! However,I am a disappointed because it seems there is a flaw. Every time she presses the ear it either doesn’t play or cuts out. Thought it was the battery but didn’t help. Got them on sale so can’t complain about but the quality for the price. She loves wearing them, despite not working properly. So that’s all that matters.

reviews.reviewTitle: Very cute for the Gabby fan
reviews.reviewText: Very impressed with this item. So much sturdier than I expected. It has a thick plastic band and the ears are made of the same durable plastic. It lights up and has multiple modes. The Gabby lover in our life loves to wear the headband while watching the show and presses the buttons to correspond with what's happening in the show. So adorable!
